<section class="py-28 md:py-40 px-5 md:px-20 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto relative overflow-hidden" id="about">
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 font-serif text-[clamp(5rem,15vw,14rem)] font-black uppercase text-white/[0.03] tracking-[-0.04em] pointer-events-none select-none whitespace-nowrap">LOKOS</div>
  <div class="relative z-10">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-white/[0.08] shrink-0">
        <img src="/hero.png" alt="Levente" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top grayscale" />
      </div>
      <p class="font-sans text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[var(--highlight)]" data-i18n="about.label">About the Artist</p>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,4rem)] font-bold text-[var(--text)] mb-12 leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em]">
      <span data-i18n="about.title1">The Architect</span><br/><span class="text-[var(--accent)] italic" data-i18n="about.title2">Behind</span> <span data-i18n="about.title3">the Code.</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-6">
      <div class="font-sans text-base text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p data-i18n="about.p1">I'm Levente, a first-year Programming Informatics student at PTE who believes code should be crafted, not just written. I build full-stack applications with Angular, Spring Boot, and Astro — always chasing that perfect balance of form and function.</p>
        <p data-i18n="about.p2">My journey started with a fascination for how things work, and it evolved into a passion for creating digital experiences that leave a lasting impact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="font-sans text-base text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p class="italic border-l-2 border-[var(--accent-dim)] pl-4 text-[var(--accent-light)]" data-i18n="about.quote">Beyond the terminal, I'm a skater, coffee nerd, and volleyball player. I believe that creativity isn't confined to a screen; it's a way of experiencing the world.</p>
        <p data-i18n="about.p3">Whether I'm exploring a new city, dialing in the perfect espresso, or skating through Pécs at golden hour — I'm always looking for that next thing that makes me feel something.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>